Package: polygone
Type: Package
Title: Functions for manipulating polygon and linestring data in R
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Sixten Maxmillian Thestrup
Maintainer: Sixten Maximillian Thestrup <smth@build.aau.dk>
Description: This package is an extension of existing packages such as sf and
    lwgeom. The aim is to simplify common tasks carried out on spatial data such
    as computing contiguities, determine leaf nodes and merging polygons.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.1.2
Imports:
    dplyr,
    future.apply,
    lwgeom,
    magrittr,
    sf
